pme.ai.fhe.de.studybuddy.model

Class UserData

  • java.lang.Object
    • pme.ai.fhe.de.studybuddy.model.UserData

  • public class UserData
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the user data entity. It stores all relevant data about the user. That would be, the city id, the university id as well as the course id, the user chose. The semester he is in and the id of the current semester as well as a the last login.
